quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alif – Laam – Meem. (Mavara aya ndemamwe ezviratidzo zvaAllah, uye hapana kana ani anoziva zvaanoreva kusara kwavo)"
  29,2,Asi vanhu vanofunga kuti vachangosiiwa vakadaro nekuti vataura kuti “Tinotenda” uye vasina kumboedzwa
  29,3,Uye zvirokwazvo takave tinoedza avo vaive mumashure mavo. Uye Allah vachaita kuti chokwadi cheavo vari muchokwadi chizivikanwe. Uye vachaita kuti manyepo evanyepi ave anozivikanzwa. (Kunyangwe Allah vachiziva zvese vasati vavaedza)
  29,4,Kana kuti vanoita zvakaipa vanofunga kuti vachatinzvenga? Hapana kana nechisvinu pane izvo zvavanofunga
  29,5,"Uyo anotarisira kusangana naAllah, zvirokwazvo, nguva yaAllah inotosvika, uye ndivo vanonzwa zvese, vanoziva zvese"
  29,6,"Uye uyo anoshanda nesimba (achirwisa), zvirokwazvo, anenge achizvishandira pachake. Zvirokwazvo, Allah havana kana nechavanoda kubva kuzvisikwa zvose (vanhu, maJinn nezvose zviripo)"
  29,7,"Uye avo vanotenda (muIslaam) uye voita mabasa akanaka, zvirokwazvo, tichave tinoregerera zvitadzo zvavo, uye tovapa mubairo unoenderana nezvakanaka zvavaiita"
  29,8,"Uye takave tinokomekedza munhu kuti ave anoita mabasa akanaka uye nekuteerera vabereki vake; asi kana vakakumanikidza kusanganisa ini nezvimwe pakunamata, pamusoro peizvo hauna ruzivo nazvo, aiwa usavatevedzere. Kwandiri muchadzoka, uye ndichave ndinokuudzai izvo zvamaiita"
  29,9,"Uye avo vanotenda (muIslaam) uye vachiita mabasa akanaka, zvirokwazvo, tichaita kuti vave vanopinda (muParadhiso) pamwechete nevanoita mabasa akanaka"
  29,10,"Muvanhu mune vamwe vanoti: “Tinotenda muna Allah.” Asi akawana dambudziko munzira yaAllah, anobva aona kunge muedzo wevanhu semarwadzo aAllah; uye kana kukunda kukauya kubva kuna Tenzi vako, (vanyengedzi) vanobva vati: “Zvirokwazvo, taive pamwechete (tichikubatsirai).” Asi Allah havazive here zviri mumoyo yevanhu nemaJinn"
  29,11,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoziva avo vanotenda, uye zvirokwazvo, vanoziva avo vanonyengedza"
  29,12,"Avo vasingatendi vanoti kune avo vanotenda: “Teverai nzira yedu tichave tinotakura zvitadzo zvenyu.” Havasi kuzombotakura zvitadzo zvavo. Zvirokwazvo, ava vanyepi"
  29,13,"Zvirokwazvo, vachatakura mabasa avo akaipa, uye vachatakura mamwe asiri avo, uye zvirokwazvo, pazuva rekutongwa vachave vanobvunzwa maererano nezvavaiwedzeredza"
  29,14,"Zvirokwazvo, takatumira Nowa kuvanhu vake, uye akagara navo kwemakore mazana mapfumbamwe nemakumi mashanu (950) (achivashevedza kuti vatende kuhumwechete hwaAllah). Nokudaro vakaparadzwa nemapopoma emvura apo vainge vasingatendi"
  29,15,"Naizvozvo takamununura (Nowa) uye nevaiva naye mungarava, uye takaita kuti (ngarava) ive chiratidzo kuvanhu nemaJinn (zvisikwa zvakasikwa nemoto)"
  29,16,"(Rangarirai) apo Abrahamu akaudza vanhu vake kuti: “Namatai Allah (Voga), uye movatya. Izvi ndizvo zvakakunakirai kana muchiziva.”"
  29,17,"“Zvirokwazvo, murikunamata zvidhori kunze kwaAllah, uye murikuwedzeredza manyepo. Zvirokwazvo, izvo zvamunonamata kunze kwaAllah hazvina kana nemasimba ekukupai raramo yenyu. Naizvozvo tsvakayi raramo yenyu kubva kuna Allah chete, uye vanamatei vari voga, uye mova munovatenda. Kwavari ndiko kwamuchadzorerwa.”"
  29,18,"“Uye kana mukaramba, zvirokwazvo, madzinza aive mumashure menyu akaramba (vatumwa vavo). Uye basa remuporofita ndere kusvitsa shoko zvakakwana zviripachena.”"
  29,19,"Havaoni here matangiro akaita Allah chisikwa, nekuchidzokorora (kuchisika). Zvirokwazvo, kuna Allah zvinhu zvidukusa"
  29,20,"Taura (Muhammad (SAW) kuti): “Fambai munyika moona sikiro yakaita Allah zvisikwa zvekare. Uye Allah vachaunza zvisikwa zvose zvehupenyu hwemangwana (vachazvimutsa mushure merufu). Zvirokwazvo, Allah vane masimba pamusoro pezvinhu zvose.”"
  29,21,"Vanorwadzisa wavanoda, uye vanoratidza tsitsi wavanoda. Zvekare kwavari ndiko kwamuchadzorerwa"
  29,22,Uye hamukwanisi kutiza Allah pano pasi zvimwechetezvo nekudenga. Zvekare hamumbowani mubatsiri kana muchengeti kusara kwaAllah
  29,23,"Uye avo vanoramba kutenda mundima dzaAllah zvekare nekusangana navo, ndeavo vasisina tarisiro yekuwana tsitsi dzangu, uye ndivo vachazowana mutongo wakaomarara unorwadza"
  29,24,"Nokudaro hapana mhinduro yakabva kuvanhu vaIbrahim (Abrahamu) kusara kwekuti: “Muurayei kana kumupisa.” Naizvozvo Allah vakamununura kubva kumoto. Zvirokwazvo, mazviri mune zviratidzo kuvanhu vanotenda"
  29,25,"Uye Ibrahim (Abrahamu) akati: “Murikutora zviumbwa (mukunamata) kunze kwaAllah. Rudo rwenyu nderwe pano pasi chete. Asi pazuva rekumutswa muchavengana (mucharambana) mega mega, uye muchatsvinyirana pachenyu. Naizvozvo nzvimbo yenyu ichange iri kumoto, zvekare muchange musina kana vabatsiri.”"